Class::ConfigMgr - A base class for implementing a singleton
object configuration manager.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries: 
	Class::ErrorHandler

